1. *Uhvatimo* se za ruke i krenimo zajedno. (Let's *hold* hands and go together.)
2. Kada *uhvatimo* ribu, odemo na ručak. (When we *catch* a fish, we go for lunch.)
3. Nadam se da ćemo uskoro *uhvatiti* priliku za druženje. (I hope we will soon *seize* an opportunity to hang out.)
4. *Uhvatila* me je panika kada sam shvatila da sam zaboravila ključeve u autu. (I was *gripped* by panic when I realized I left my keys in the car.)
5. Moramo brzo *uhvatiti* autobus ako želimo stići na vrijeme. (We need to quickly *catch* the bus if we want to arrive on time.)
6. Kada *uhvatimo* lopova, pozovemo policiju. (When we *apprehend* a thief, we call the police.)
7. *Uhvatili* smo se u koštac sa problemom i uspješno ga riješili. (We *tackled* the problem head-on and successfully solved it.)
8. Molim te, *uhvati* ovaj paket i stavi ga na stol. (Please, *grab* this package and put it on the table.)
9. Kada *uhvatimo* snove, možemo ih ostvariti. (When we *grasp* our dreams, we can achieve them.)
10. *Uhvatim* sebe da razmišljam o tebi često. (I *find* myself thinking about you often.)